#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:363
msgid ""
"Select which post statuses are accessible when visiting a PublishPress "
"shortlink."
msgstr ""
"Pasirinkite, kurie įrašų statusai yra pasiekiami, kai lankotės PublishPress "
"trumpąja nuoroda."

